<div class="container-fluid welcome">
    <div class="container words">
        <p class="title">Welcome to the Lake Inn!</p>
        <div class="icon-title">
            <img src="~/Content/img/img/icon-title.png">
        </div>
        <p class="short-des">We are pleased to be your premier breakfast and bed for rest, activities and nature on Beautiful Lake.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container images">
        <p class="short-des">We are pleased to be your premier breakfast and bed for rest, activities and nature on Beautiful Lake.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-12 col-md-12 itemBox" style="height: 400px;">
                <div class="item" style="background-image: url(Content/img/img/greeting-img1.jpg);"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-xl-12 col-lg-6 col-md-12 itemBox" style="height: 200px;">
                        <div class="item" style="background-image: url(Content/img/img/greeting-img2.jpg);"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-xl-12 col-lg-6 col-md-12 itemBox" style="height: 200px;">
                        <div class="item" style="background-image: url(Content/img/img/greeting-img3.jpg);"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container detail">
        <p>Smithhammer House at Terry Point is the perfect New Hampshire Inn. with nature at our doorstep and many attractions nearby. On our scenic, quiet property, you will be treated to idyllic views of Beautiful Lake and its glistening water, our guardian mountains in the distance and luscious gardens.</p>
